claw.shenron.translator

Class AnalyzedPragma

  • java.lang.Object
    • claw.shenron.translator.AnalyzedPragma
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClawPragma

    public class AnalyzedPragma
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for any analyzed pragma. This object is then passed to a transformation. Base implementation only stores the raw pragma element object.
    Author:
    clementval
